# Groq Chat Completions API test
# How to use:
# 1) Export your key in terminal: export GROQ_API_KEY="your_key"
# 2) Open this file in VS Code and use REST Client "Send Request"
#    (or copy the request as curl)

@baseUrl = https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions
@apiKey = ''

### Basic check (your requested prompt)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "model": "llama-3.1-8b-instant",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Explain Bitcoin in simple terms"
    }
  ]
}

### JSON-mode style response test (matches app-like usage)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "model": "llama3-8b-8192",
  "temperature": 0.4,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a concise financial education assistant."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Explain Bitcoin in simple terms and include one caution point."
    }
  ]
}
